<h2 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:16pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:24pt; margin-bottom:12pt; border-bottom:2px solid #000; padding-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">Abstract</h2>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Academic institutions manage massive amounts of student information, including attendance registers, grading books, assignment submissions, class schedules, and announcement feeds. Frequently, these data systems are fragmented, making it difficult for students to monitor their overall progress or understand their placement eligibility.</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">This project report describes the design and development of <strong>AcadTrack</strong>, a centralized web platform designed to solve this data fragmentation. AcadTrack is built on the <strong>MERN (MongoDB, Express.js, React.js, Node.js)</strong> architecture and provides secure, role-based interfaces for Students, Faculty, and Administrators.</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">To protect sensitive grade and attendance records, AcadTrack implements a two-step authentication system. This system combines bcryptjs password hashing and JSON Web Tokens (JWT) for stateless sessions with One-Time Passwords (OTP) delivered securely via the Brevo HTTPS REST API.</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Key features include:</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">1.  <strong>Placement Eligibility Evaluator:</strong> An engine that aggregates course grades, backlog data, and lecture attendance to evaluate placement readiness in real time.</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">2.  <strong>Visual Timetable Scheduler:</strong> A scheduling dashboard that detects and prevents classroom booking conflicts.</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">3.  <strong>Core Educational Modules:</strong> Features for managing attendance registers, hosting assignments, grading submissions, and distributing targeted announcements.</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">The system was evaluated using modular integration tests, role-based boundary validations, and conflict-detection scenarios, demonstrating high reliability and secure operations.</p>

<br style="page-break-before:always; clear:both;" /><hr style="border:0; border-top:1px solid #cbd5e1; margin:24px 0;" />

