<h2 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:16pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:24pt; margin-bottom:12pt; border-bottom:2px solid #000; padding-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">Chapter 1: Introduction</h2>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">1.1 Context and Background</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Higher education institutions manage complex academic environments containing hundreds of courses, dozens of departments, and thousands of students. Keeping track of student progress, marks, attendance, assignments, and announcements is crucial for institutional operations.</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Historically, this information was recorded manually on paper ledger books or spreadsheets. Over time, these records transitioned to various independent software tools. Today, this fragmentation makes it difficult for administrators to monitor operations and prevents students from easily tracking their academic status.</p>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">1.2 Problem Statement</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Traditional academic tracking systems suffer from several main issues:</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">1.  <strong>Data Fragmentation:</strong> Academic files, attendance sheets, and assignment submissions are kept in separate databases, making it difficult to generate a unified view of student progress.</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">2.  <strong>Lack of Real-Time Analytics:</strong> Students are often unaware of their placement eligibility status until the final semester, leaving them unable to take corrective action early.</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">3.  <strong>Vulnerability to Data Tampering:</strong> Systems without multi-step verification and role-based access control are vulnerable to unauthorized changes in grades or attendance records.</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">4.  <strong>Timetable Booking Conflicts:</strong> Manual scheduling processes often lead to double-booked classrooms or instructors, disrupting daily operations.</p>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">1.3 Objective and Goals</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">The primary objective of this project is to develop <strong>AcadTrack</strong>, a unified platform that integrates student academic records, attendance sheets, assignment submissions, class schedules, and notices.</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">The project aims to achieve the following goals:</p>
<ul style="margin-bottom:12pt; margin-left:20px;"><li>  Build a responsive web application that aggregates student performance metrics.</li>
<li>  Implement a real-time placement eligibility evaluator based on GPA, attendance, and backlog data.</li>
<li>  Create an automated timetable scheduler that detects and blocks booking conflicts.</li>
<li>  Secure the platform using role-based access control, hashed passwords, and email-based OTP verification.</li>
</ul>
<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">1.4 Scope and Stakeholder Analysis</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">The system supports three user roles:</p>
<ul style="margin-bottom:12pt; margin-left:20px;"><li>  <strong>Students:</strong> Can view their GPA trends, course attendance, assignments, notices, and placement eligibility.</li>
<li>  <strong>Faculty Members:</strong> Can take attendance, submit grades, post assignments, and publish notices.</li>
<li>  <strong>Administrators:</strong> Can manage user profiles, assign faculty to courses, and configure global academic settings.</li>
</ul>
<br style="page-break-before:always; clear:both;" /><hr style="border:0; border-top:1px solid #cbd5e1; margin:24px 0;" />

<h2 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:16pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:24pt; margin-bottom:12pt; border-bottom:2px solid #000; padding-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">Chapter 2: Literature Review &amp; Technology Stack</h2>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">2.1 Evolution of Academic Software Systems</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Early academic management systems relied on mainframes to maintain student files, which required batch processing and offered limited user accessibility. The transition to client-server desktop applications improved access for administrative staff but remained unavailable to students and faculty.</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Modern web architectures have enabled real-time web applications. These platforms allow students, faculty, and administrators to interact on a single system, ensuring database consistency and immediate access to information.</p>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">2.2 MERN Stack Architecture Overview</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">AcadTrack uses the MERN stack to leverage JavaScript throughout the entire development process:</p>
<ul style="margin-bottom:12pt; margin-left:20px;"><li>  <strong>React.js (Frontend):</strong> Builds a responsive, single-page application interface. State changes trigger targeted updates to components without reloading the page, which is useful for displaying dynamic charts.</li>
<li>  <strong>Node.js &amp; Express.js (Backend):</strong> Node.js provides a non-blocking, event-driven runtime environment that handles concurrent API requests efficiently. Express.js simplifies routing, middleware integration, and request handling.</li>
<li>  <strong>MongoDB (Database):</strong> A document-oriented NoSQL database that stores data in BSON format. This structure accommodates nested academic records, such as lists of graded courses, without requiring complex SQL joins.</li>
</ul>
<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">2.3 Mongoose ODM and NoSQL Advantages</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Mongoose acts as an Object Document Mapper (ODM) for MongoDB, bridging the gap between raw document data and JavaScript objects. It enables developers to define strict schemas, default values, validators, and virtual properties, combining the flexibility of NoSQL with schema enforcement. This is useful for validating grade values, email formats, and role constraints on the database level.</p>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">2.4 Security and Verification Technologies</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">To secure academic records, the platform implements several security standards:</p>
<ul style="margin-bottom:12pt; margin-left:20px;"><li>  <strong>bcryptjs:</strong> Salts and hashes passwords before saving them, protecting credentials against reverse-engineering.</li>
<li>  <strong>JSON Web Tokens (JWT):</strong> Generates encrypted session tokens that the client attaches to HTTP headers. This allows the backend to verify requests without keeping session states in memory.</li>
<li>  <strong>Brevo HTTPS API:</strong> Used to send transaction emails for OTP verification, bypassing local SMTP port blocks to ensure reliable email delivery.</li>
</ul>
<br style="page-break-before:always; clear:both;" /><hr style="border:0; border-top:1px solid #cbd5e1; margin:24px 0;" />

<h2 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:16pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:24pt; margin-bottom:12pt; border-bottom:2px solid #000; padding-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">Chapter 3: System Feasibility Analysis</h2>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">3.1 Technical Feasibility</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">The technologies used—React, Node.js, and MongoDB—are well-documented and widely supported. Mongoose provides schema validation, while Tailwind CSS simplifies building responsive user interfaces. Using the Brevo API ensures reliable delivery of OTP codes, making the technical implementation highly feasible.</p>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">3.2 Operational Feasibility</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">The platform is designed with role-specific views to simplify workflows. Administrators manage the user directory, faculty control attendance registers and assignment grading, and students track their academic metrics. This clear separation of concerns reduces usability hurdles and makes the system operationally feasible.</p>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">3.3 Economic Feasibility</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">The platform is built on open-source technologies, eliminating licensing fees. It can be deployed on standard cloud services and scaled as needed, which keeps initial hosting and maintenance costs low.</p>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">3.4 Legal and Social Feasibility</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">The system protects user data using password encryption, role-based access control, and email verification. It supports academic integrity by securing grading logs, aligning with student data privacy guidelines and making the system socially feasible.</p>

<br style="page-break-before:always; clear:both;" /><hr style="border:0; border-top:1px solid #cbd5e1; margin:24px 0;" />

<h2 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:16pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:24pt; margin-bottom:12pt; border-bottom:2px solid #000; padding-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">Chapter 4: Software Requirements Specification (SRS)</h2>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">4.1 Product Perspective and Constraints</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">AcadTrack operates as a secure web portal connecting to a Node.js backend. The client application runs in modern web browsers and requires an active internet connection to interact with the backend API and database.</p>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">4.2 Functional Requirements</h3>

<h4 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">4.2.1 Authentication &amp; Profile Verification (FR-01)</h4>
<ul style="margin-bottom:12pt; margin-left:20px;"><li>  <strong>Registration:</strong> Users must provide a name, email, password, role, department, and ID.</li>
<li>  <strong>OTP Verification:</strong> The system must generate a 6-digit OTP code during registration or login, email it to the user, and verify it within 5 minutes.</li>
<li>  <strong>Role Identification:</strong> Set roles to <code style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:2px 4px; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; color:#4c1d95;">student</code>, <code style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:2px 4px; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; color:#4c1d95;">faculty</code>, or <code style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:2px 4px; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; color:#4c1d95;">admin</code> to restrict access to specific features.</li>
</ul>
<h4 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">4.2.2 Student Progress Analytics (FR-02)</h4>
<ul style="margin-bottom:12pt; margin-left:20px;"><li>  <strong>Academic Summaries:</strong> Calculate overall CGPA, earned credits, attendance rates, and backlog counts.</li>
<li>  <strong>Visual Charts:</strong> Render interactive charts showing SGPA and CGPA trends over semesters.</li>
<li>  <strong>Placement Checker:</strong> Evaluate placement eligibility automatically based on the student's academic records.</li>
</ul>
<h4 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">4.2.3 Timetable and Schedule Planner (FR-03)</h4>
<ul style="margin-bottom:12pt; margin-left:20px;"><li>  <strong>Grid Display:</strong> Render a weekly calendar showing scheduled classes, timings, and classrooms.</li>
<li>  <strong>Conflict Prevention:</strong> Check schedule entries to ensure no classroom is double-booked on the same day and time.</li>
<li>  <strong>Custom Views:</strong> Limit student views to enrolled courses and faculty views to assigned teaching slots.</li>
</ul>
<h4 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">4.2.4 Lecture Attendance Tracker (FR-04)</h4>
<ul style="margin-bottom:12pt; margin-left:20px;"><li>  <strong>Marking:</strong> Allow faculty to record student attendance for specific course dates.</li>
<li>  <strong>Daily Constraint:</strong> Restrict attendance entries to one registry per course per day.</li>
<li>  <strong>Aggregation:</strong> Calculate subject-specific and overall attendance percentages for students.</li>
</ul>
<h4 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">4.2.5 Assignment &amp; Grading Portal (FR-05)</h4>
<ul style="margin-bottom:12pt; margin-left:20px;"><li>  <strong>Assignment Publishing:</strong> Allow faculty to post assignments with descriptions and reference documents.</li>
<li>  <strong>PDF Submissions:</strong> Allow students to upload PDF files for assignments before the due date.</li>
<li>  <strong>Grading interface:</strong> Provide a interface for faculty to grade submissions and leave feedback.</li>
</ul>
<h4 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">4.2.6 Announcement Notice Board (FR-06)</h4>
<ul style="margin-bottom:12pt; margin-left:20px;"><li>  <strong>Notices:</strong> Allow admins and faculty to write and publish notices.</li>
<li>  <strong>Targeting:</strong> Filter notices based on the intended audience (e.g., student or faculty).</li>
</ul>
<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">4.3 Non-Functional Requirements</h3>

<h4 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">4.3.1 Security &amp; Access Controls (NFR-01)</h4>
<ul style="margin-bottom:12pt; margin-left:20px;"><li>  Encrypt all passwords using <code style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:2px 4px; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; color:#4c1d95;">bcryptjs</code>.</li>
<li>  Validate requests on the server using JWT signature checks.</li>
<li>  Restrict API routes using role-based authorization rules.</li>
</ul>
<h4 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">4.3.2 System Performance &amp; Latency (NFR-02)</h4>
<ul style="margin-bottom:12pt; margin-left:20px;"><li>  Ensure backend API response times remain under 200ms.</li>
<li>  Optimize database queries using targeted indexes.</li>
<li>  Load frontend components efficiently by caching assets on the client.</li>
</ul>
<h4 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">4.3.3 Reliability &amp; Database Constraints (NFR-03)</h4>
<ul style="margin-bottom:12pt; margin-left:20px;"><li>  Enforce schema constraints and unique indexes to prevent duplicate entries.</li>
<li>  Manage transaction status to ensure data consistency during updates.</li>
</ul>
<h4 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">4.3.4 Usability &amp; Device Responsiveness (NFR-04)</h4>
<ul style="margin-bottom:12pt; margin-left:20px;"><li>  Implement a responsive web interface using Tailwind CSS.</li>
<li>  Support modern web browsers (Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Edge).</li>
</ul>
<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">4.4 Hardware and Software Interfaces</h3>
<ul style="margin-bottom:12pt; margin-left:20px;"><li>  <strong>Software Interfaces:</strong> Connects to MongoDB via Mongoose and integrates with the Brevo API to send transactional emails.</li>
<li>  <strong>User Interfaces:</strong> Features responsive HTML5 pages styled with Tailwind CSS, utilizing Lucide React for iconography.</li>
</ul>
<br style="page-break-before:always; clear:both;" /><hr style="border:0; border-top:1px solid #cbd5e1; margin:24px 0;" />

<h2 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:16pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:24pt; margin-bottom:12pt; border-bottom:2px solid #000; padding-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">Chapter 5: System Design &amp; UML Modeling</h2>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">5.1 High-Level Architecture</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">AcadTrack follows a decoupled three-tier model where the client layer communicates with the server layer via JSON payloads over HTTPS:</p>

<pre style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:12px; border:1px solid #cbd5e1; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; white-space:pre-wrap;"><code>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">[React Client App] &lt;---HTTPS/JSON---&gt; [Express / Node Web Server] &lt;---Mongoose ODM---&gt; [MongoDB Cluster]</p>
</code></pre>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">5.2 Data Flow Diagram (DFD Level 1)</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">This diagram shows the flow of information between users, system processes, and the database:</p>

<div style="background:#fafafa; border:1px solid #e2e8f0; padding:10px; margin:10px 0; font-family:sans-serif; font-size:9pt; text-align:center; color:#475569;"><strong>[UML/Mermaid Diagram]</strong><pre style="text-align:left; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:9.5pt;">
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">graph TD</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">User([User])</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">AuthProc[1.0 Session Auth &amp; OTP]</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">CourseProc[2.0 Course &amp; Enrollment]</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">GradingProc[3.0 Grading &amp; GPA Calculations]</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">AttendProc[4.0 Attendance Tracker]</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">SchedProc[5.0 Schedule Management]</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">DB[(MongoDB Database)]</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Mailer[Brevo Mailer]</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">User --&gt;|Login Credentials| AuthProc</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">AuthProc --&gt;|Send OTP Code| Mailer</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">AuthProc &lt;==&gt;|Verify &amp; Query Session| DB</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">AuthProc --&gt;|JWT Token| User</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">User --&gt;|Manage Course/User| CourseProc</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">CourseProc &lt;==&gt;|Write Course Details| DB</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">User --&gt;|Grade Marks| GradingProc</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">GradingProc &lt;==&gt;|Update AcademicRecord| DB</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">User --&gt;|Submit Attendance Sheet| AttendProc</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">AttendProc &lt;==&gt;|Write Attendance| DB</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">User --&gt;|Create Timetable Slot| SchedProc</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">SchedProc &lt;==&gt;|Write Schedule Slot| DB</p>
</pre></div>

<br style="page-break-before:always; clear:both;" /><hr style="border:0; border-top:1px solid #cbd5e1; margin:24px 0;" />

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">5.3 UML Use Case Modeling</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Use case modeling defines user interactions and system boundaries:</p>

<ul style="margin-bottom:12pt; margin-left:20px;"><li>  <strong>Administrator Cases:</strong> Admin users manage user profiles, allocate courses, and configure global system settings.</li>
<li>  <strong>Faculty Cases:</strong> Faculty members mark attendance sheets, create assignments, grade student submissions, and write notices.</li>
<li>  <strong>Student Cases:</strong> Students view their dashboard stats, check notice board announcements, and upload assignment files.</li>
</ul>
<br style="page-break-before:always; clear:both;" /><hr style="border:0; border-top:1px solid #cbd5e1; margin:24px 0;" />

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">5.4 UML Class Diagram</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">The class diagram shows the structure of the system's database entities and their associations:</p>

<div style="background:#fafafa; border:1px solid #e2e8f0; padding:10px; margin:10px 0; font-family:sans-serif; font-size:9pt; text-align:center; color:#475569;"><strong>[UML/Mermaid Diagram]</strong><pre style="text-align:left; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:9.5pt;">
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">classDiagram</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">class User {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+ObjectId id</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+string name</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+string email</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+string password</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+string role</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+string studentId</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+string facultyId</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+string department</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+number semester</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+matchPassword()</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">}</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">class Course {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+ObjectId id</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+string name</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+string code</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+number credits</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+string department</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+ObjectId faculty</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+array studentsEnrolled</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">}</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">class AcademicRecord {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+ObjectId id</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+ObjectId student</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+number semester</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+array courses</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+number sgpa</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+number cgpa</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">}</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">class Attendance {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+ObjectId id</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+ObjectId course</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+date date</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+array records</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">}</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">class Assignment {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+ObjectId id</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+string title</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+string description</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+ObjectId course</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+date dueDate</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+string fileUrl</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">}</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">class Submission {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+ObjectId id</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+ObjectId assignment</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+ObjectId student</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+string fileUrl</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+date submittedAt</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+string grade</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+string feedback</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+string status</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">}</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">class Schedule {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+ObjectId id</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+ObjectId course</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+string dayOfWeek</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+string startTime</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+string endTime</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">+string classroom</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">}</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">User "1" --&gt; "*" Course : teaches / enrolled</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">User "1" --&gt; "*" AcademicRecord : owns</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Course "1" --&gt; "*" Attendance : logs</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Course "1" --&gt; "*" Assignment : has</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Assignment "1" --&gt; "*" Submission : receives</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">User "1" --&gt; "*" Submission : submits</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Course "1" --&gt; "*" Schedule : runs_on</p>
</pre></div>

<br style="page-break-before:always; clear:both;" /><hr style="border:0; border-top:1px solid #cbd5e1; margin:24px 0;" />

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">5.5 UML Sequence Diagram: Authentication &amp; OTP Verification</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">The sequence of events during a login request and OTP verification:</p>

<div style="background:#fafafa; border:1px solid #e2e8f0; padding:10px; margin:10px 0; font-family:sans-serif; font-size:9pt; text-align:center; color:#475569;"><strong>[UML/Mermaid Diagram]</strong><pre style="text-align:left; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:9.5pt;">
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">sequenceDiagram</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">autonumber</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">actor User as User Agent</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">participant Client as React SPA Client</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">participant API as Express API Server</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">participant DB as MongoDB Cluster</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">participant Mailer as Brevo Mailer</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">User-&gt;&gt;Client: Enter Credentials</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Client-&gt;&gt;API: POST /api/auth/login-request</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">API-&gt;&gt;DB: Find User by Email</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">DB--&gt;&gt;API: User Record (Hashed Password)</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">API-&gt;&gt;API: Verify Password Hashing</p>
    
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">alt Credentials Valid</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">API-&gt;&gt;API: Generate 6-Digit OTP &amp; Save Session</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">API-&gt;&gt;DB: Save OTP Document (TTL 5m)</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">API-&gt;&gt;Mailer: Send Transactional Email request</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Mailer--&gt;&gt;User: Deliver OTP Verification Email</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">API--&gt;&gt;Client: Return OTP Sent Status (200)</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Client--&gt;&gt;User: Display Verification Screen</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">else Credentials Invalid</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">API--&gt;&gt;Client: Return 401 Unauthorized Error</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Client--&gt;&gt;User: Display Invalid Credentials Alert</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">end</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">User-&gt;&gt;Client: Input 6-Digit OTP</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Client-&gt;&gt;API: POST /api/auth/verify-otp (email, code)</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">API-&gt;&gt;DB: Find and Match OTP Document</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">DB--&gt;&gt;API: OTP Match Status</p>
    
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">alt OTP Valid &amp; Not Expired</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">API-&gt;&gt;API: Generate JSON Web Token (JWT)</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">API--&gt;&gt;Client: Return JWT Token &amp; Profile Info (200)</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Client-&gt;&gt;Client: Cache JWT in LocalStorage</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Client--&gt;&gt;User: Redirect to Role Dashboard</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">else OTP Invalid / Expired</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">API--&gt;&gt;Client: Return 400 Bad Request</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Client--&gt;&gt;User: Display OTP Invalid Alert</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">end</p>
</pre></div>

<br style="page-break-before:always; clear:both;" /><hr style="border:0; border-top:1px solid #cbd5e1; margin:24px 0;" />

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">5.6 UML Activity Diagram: Placement Eligibility Engine</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">This diagram illustrates the step-by-step logic used to calculate a student's placement eligibility:</p>

<div style="background:#fafafa; border:1px solid #e2e8f0; padding:10px; margin:10px 0; font-family:sans-serif; font-size:9pt; text-align:center; color:#475569;"><strong>[UML/Mermaid Diagram]</strong><pre style="text-align:left; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:9.5pt;">
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">flowchart TD</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Start([Start Evaluation]) --&gt; FetchData[Fetch Student Profile &amp; Academic History]</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">FetchData --&gt; CheckCGPA{Is CGPA &gt;= 7.0?}</p>
    
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">CheckCGPA -- No --&gt; SetIneligible[Set Eligible = False]</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">CheckCGPA -- Yes --&gt; FetchAttendance[Calculate Overall Attendance Percentage]</p>
    
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">FetchAttendance --&gt; CheckAtt{Is Attendance &gt;= 75%?}</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">CheckAtt -- No --&gt; SetIneligible</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">CheckAtt -- Yes --&gt; FetchGrades[Scan Records for Grade F]</p>
    
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">FetchGrades --&gt; CheckBacklogs{Any Backlogs Found?}</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">CheckBacklogs -- Yes --&gt; SetIneligible</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">CheckBacklogs -- No --&gt; SetEligible[Set Eligible = True]</p>
    
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">SetIneligible --&gt; OutputResult[Return Status and Criteria Metrics]</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">SetEligible --&gt; OutputResult</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">OutputResult --&gt; End([End Evaluation])</p>
</pre></div>

<br style="page-break-before:always; clear:both;" /><hr style="border:0; border-top:1px solid #cbd5e1; margin:24px 0;" />

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">5.7 Entity-Relationship Diagram (ERD) &amp; Database Relations</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">This diagram details entity relationships, primary keys, and foreign keys:</p>

<div style="background:#fafafa; border:1px solid #e2e8f0; padding:10px; margin:10px 0; font-family:sans-serif; font-size:9pt; text-align:center; color:#475569;"><strong>[UML/Mermaid Diagram]</strong><pre style="text-align:left; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:9.5pt;">
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">erDiagram</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">USER ||--o{ ACADEMIC_RECORD : owns</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">USER ||--o{ COURSE : teaches_or_enrolled</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">COURSE ||--o{ ATTENDANCE : tracks</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">COURSE ||--o{ ASSIGNMENT : holds</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">ASSIGNMENT ||--o{ SUBMISSION : receives</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">USER ||--o{ SUBMISSION : uploads</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">COURSE ||--o{ SCHEDULE : schedules</p>

<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">USER {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">ObjectId id PK</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">string name</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">string email</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">string password</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">string role</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">string studentId</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">string facultyId</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">string department</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">number semester</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">}</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">COURSE {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">ObjectId id PK</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">string name</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">string code</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">number credits</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">string department</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">ObjectId faculty FK</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">}</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">ACADEMIC_RECORD {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">ObjectId id PK</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">ObjectId student FK</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">number semester</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">number sgpa</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">number cgpa</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">}</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">ATTENDANCE {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">ObjectId id PK</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">ObjectId course FK</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">date date</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">}</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">ASSIGNMENT {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">ObjectId id PK</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">string title</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">string description</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">ObjectId course FK</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">date dueDate</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">string fileUrl</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">}</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">SUBMISSION {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">ObjectId id PK</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">ObjectId assignment FK</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">ObjectId student FK</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">string fileUrl</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">date submittedAt</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">string grade</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">string feedback</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">string status</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">}</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">SCHEDULE {</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">ObjectId id PK</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">ObjectId course FK</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">string dayOfWeek</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">string startTime</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">string endTime</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">string classroom</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">}</p>
</pre></div>

<br style="page-break-before:always; clear:both;" /><hr style="border:0; border-top:1px solid #cbd5e1; margin:24px 0;" />

<h2 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:16pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:24pt; margin-bottom:12pt; border-bottom:2px solid #000; padding-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">Chapter 6: Database Schema Design &amp; Data Dictionary</h2>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">6.1 MongoDB Modeling Principles</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">AcadTrack's database is modeled using Mongoose to balance flexibility and data validation. Relationships are maintained using ObjectIds rather than deeply nested structures, which keeps document sizes manageable and query structures clean.</p>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">6.2 Detailed Data Dictionary Tables</h3>

<h4 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">Table 6.1: Users Collection (<code style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:2px 4px; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; color:#4c1d95;">users</code>)</h4>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">Stores profile information for all system users:</p>

<table style="border-collapse:collapse; width:100%; margin:12pt 0; border:1px solid #000;"><tr style="background-color:#f8fafc;"><th style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; background-color:#f1f5f9; font-weight:bold; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:10.5pt; text-align:left;">Field Name</th><th style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; background-color:#f1f5f9; font-weight:bold; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:10.5pt; text-align:left;">Data Type</th><th style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; background-color:#f1f5f9; font-weight:bold; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:10.5pt; text-align:left;">Key Type</th><th style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; background-color:#f1f5f9; font-weight:bold; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:10.5pt; text-align:left;">Nullable</th><th style="border:1px solid #000; padding:6px; background-color:#f1f5f9; font-weight:bold; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:10.5pt; text-align:left;">Description / Constraints</th></tr>

