<h4 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">Table 6.3: Attendance Collection (<code style="background:#f1f5f9; padding:2px 4px; font-family:Consolas,monospace; font-size:10pt; color:#4c1d95;">attendances</code>)</h4>
