<br style="page-break-before:always; clear:both;" /><hr style="border:0; border-top:1px solid #cbd5e1; margin:24px 0;" />

<h2 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:16pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:24pt; margin-bottom:12pt; border-bottom:2px solid #000; padding-bottom:4pt; page-break-after:avoid;">Chapter 10: Future Scope &amp; Conclusion</h2>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">10.1 Future Scope and Extensibility</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">AcadTrack is built on an extensible architecture that supports future feature integrations:</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">1.  <strong>Real-Time Notifications:</strong> Adding WebSocket support (via Socket.io) would allow the system to send instant alerts for timetable changes, announcements, and grade releases.</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">2.  <strong>AI-Based Performance Analysis:</strong> Incorporating machine learning tools could help analyze historical student data to identify students who may need additional academic support.</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">3.  <strong>Integrated Recruiting Portal:</strong> Adding a recruitment module would allow companies to post job openings directly to students who meet their eligibility criteria.</p>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">10.2 Concluding Remarks</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">The <strong>AcadTrack</strong> system centralizes academic records, class schedules, assignments, and announcements. By providing role-specific views and automated tools like the Placement Eligibility Evaluator, the application helps coordinate university operations, provides clear progress tracking for students, and reduces administrative overhead.</p>

<h3 style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin-top:18pt; margin-bottom:6pt; page-break-after:avoid;">10.3 References and Bibliography</h3>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">1.  <strong>MongoDB Documentation:</strong> NoSQL Schema Design and Index Optimization. [https://docs.mongodb.com/](https://docs.mongodb.com/)</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">2.  <strong>ReactJS Community Guides:</strong> Component Architecture and Context-Based State Management. [https://react.dev/](https://react.dev/)</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">3.  <strong>Express Framework Documentation:</strong> API Routing and Middleware Implementation. [https://expressjs.com/](https://expressjs.com/)</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">4.  <strong>Internet Engineering Task Force (IETF):</strong> RFC 7519: JSON Web Tokens (JWT) Specification. [https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc7519](https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc7519)</p>
<p style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:12pt; text-align:justify; margin-bottom:12pt; line-height:1.5;">5.  <strong>Brevo REST API Developer Guides:</strong> Transactional Email Delivery. [https://developers.brevo.com/](https://developers.brevo.com/)</p>

